window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A short story by John Philips.&nbsp;</p> <p>If you had the power to raise the dead for helping and protecting others, would you use it? Even if that power comes from a macabre and twisted source?</p> <p>John, Andrew, and Kate planned for a relaxing catch-up during a weekend stay in the countryside. However, by chance, they discover a horrifying secret that allows them to raise the dead!&nbsp;</p> <p>If most people knew about this recently discovered ability, they would think it repulsive. But as their power grows, so does the sinister and unwanted attention of others.&nbsp;</p> <p>Will John, Andrew, and Kate learn how to wield their nightmarish and dark talent before itâ€™s taken from them?</p>"; 
